title: 이달의소녀탐구 #292 (LOONA TV #292)
members: HaSeul, Yves, Kim Lip, HyunJin, HeeJin
summary:
0:09 -- HaSeul is dressed up as a bird to shoot her part of the teaser. “Don’t I look like the
queen of birds?” Then she starts dancing. Yves enters while doing her Ostrich dance.
0:25 -- HyunJin PD takes over while showing LipSeul dancing. “You look like a tribal
chief, not a swan!” 2Jin feel like the birds nest is beautiful.
